### Create a new request
POST http://localhost:4003/requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "1234-uuid",
  "type": "HOSTEL_JOIN",
  "details": {
    "roomPreference": "single",
    "hostelBlock": "A"
  }
}

### Get all requests
GET http://localhost:4003/requests

### Get requests by studentId
GET http://localhost:4003/requests/student/1234-uuid

### Get request by id
GET http://localhost:4003/requests/abcd-uuid

### Update status (partial update)
PATCH http://localhost:4003/requests/abcd-uuid/status?status=APPROVED&reviewedBy=warden-uuid

### Full update (replace entire request)
PUT http://localhost:4003/requests/abcd-uuid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "1234-uuid",
  "type": "HOSTEL_LEAVE",
  "details": {
    "leaveFrom": "2025-10-10",
    "leaveTo": "2025-10-20"
  }
}

### Delete a request
DELETE http://localhost:4003/requests/abcd-uuid
